Country Codes and Income Groups of Countries and Territories

world_income.Rd

A dataset containing a row per country/territory with information on the country/territory ISO codes and income group as defined by the World Bank.

Usage

world_income

Format

A data frame with 250 rows and 5 columns:

alpha_3_code

The three digit ISO code for the country/territory

alpha_2_code

The two digit ISO code for the country/territory

numeric

The numeric ISO code for the country/territory

country

Name of country or territory

economy

Name of country or territory according to the World Bank data

income_group

Income classification of the country/territory

redcap_number

The numeric value for the country/territory in the IDDO REDCap codebook. The number in this file may not be the same in your REDCap, please ensure you check this before using this variable

Details

Dates that data was accessed on:

  • World Bank: 11/11/2024

  • ISO: 18/06/2024

  • REDCap: 15/11/2024
